room_title: Escape room "The Salem Witch Hunt" by Back in Time Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 23700 S Western Ave Harbor City, CA 90710
room_description: Back In Time has been hired by a descendant of one of the convicted women accused of witchcraft to travel back to 1692 and conduct an investigation. You and your team must gather evidence to either support or refute these accusations.
